data.description: Don't miss out on this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, boasting 1,179 square feet of comfortable living space. Impeccably clean and well-maintained, it's ready for a new owner. This home is a turnkey opportunity, convenient to show, and move-in ready. Your chance to make it yours is now!    DOG IN BACKYARD!!! Welcome to your new home in Dayton! This is a fantastic opportunity to embrace a wonderful living experience in a welcoming community. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home sweet home. This lovely home is not only charming but also conveniently located close to shopping and offers easy access to Carson City and the USA Parkway, making it a prime choice for those seeking both comfort and convenience. Don't wait, schedule a showing today! In addition to its attractive interior, this home features beautifully landscaped front and backyards. The carefully designed outdoor spaces add to the curb appeal and provide a pleasant environment for outdoor relaxation and enjoyment. It's a perfect blend of comfort and aesthetics, both inside and out!
